TODO(real-icon): replace with a real 256x256 PNG before the v0.4.5 release.

This placeholder marker file documents the missing icon. The AppImage spec
requires a top-level icon file matching the `Icon=` entry in
`forex-app.desktop`. The icon must be:

- PNG (or SVG; PNG preferred for compatibility)
- 256x256 pixels (or 512x512; appimagetool resamples for menu thumbnails)
- Filename: `forex-app.png` (matches `Icon=forex-app` in the desktop entry)
- Located at:
    packaging/appimage/forex-app.AppDir/forex-app.png            (canonical)
    packaging/appimage/forex-app.AppDir/usr/share/icons/hicolor/256x256/apps/forex-app.png

Until a real icon ships:
- `packaging/appimage/build.sh` will fail-loudly if no `forex-app.png` is
  present, pointing the operator at this TODO.
- The desktop entry remains valid; only the launcher graphic is missing.

Source for the eventual real icon: TODO(real-icon) — operator to provide.
